keyMappings:
# Insert your preferred key mappings here.

map h goBack
map l goForward
map H scrollLeft
map L scrollRight
map <c-d> scrollPageDown
map <c-f> scrollFullPageDown
map <c-b> scrollFullPageUp
map gp togglePinTab
map b Vomnibar.activateTabSelection
map dd removeTab
map <c-v> passNextKey
map <c-i> enterInsertMode
map m Marks.activateCreateMode swap
map ` Marks.activateGotoMode swap
map <m-,> moveTabLeft count=99
map <m-.> moveTabRight count=99
map \ passNextKey normal
map s Vomnibar.activate keyword=g
map w Vomnibar.activate keyword=w
map <m-b> Vomnibar.activateBookmarks
map gd LinkHints.activateModeToDownloadLink
